import {FloatingLabel, Form} from 'react-bootstrap'

export const FloatingLabelsEmail = () => {

    return <>
{/* 
        <FloatingLabel
            controlId="floatingInput"
            label="אימייל"
            className="mb-1 w-50 p-3"
        >
    
            <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" className="text-end" dir="rtl" />
    
        </FloatingLabel> */}

<Form.Floating className="mb-3">
    <Form.Control
      id="floatingInputCustom"
      type="email"
      placeholder="name@example.com"
    />
    <label htmlFor="floatingInputCustom" className="bg-primary float-right">Email address</label>
</Form.Floating>


    
    </>
}
